Description: Professional video compositor with multi-layer support
 CUEMS Video Composer is a high-performance video compositor designed
 for live video production and playback. It supports multiple video layers,
 hardware-accelerated decoding (VAAPI, CUDA, QSV), HAP codec support,
 MTC/LTC timecode synchronization, and live input sources including NDI.
 .
 Features:
  * Multi-layer video composition
  * Hardware-accelerated video decoding (Intel, NVIDIA, AMD)
  * HAP codec support with direct GPU texture upload
  * MTC/LTC timecode synchronization
  * NDI input support (requires NDI SDK)
  * V4L2 and network stream support
  * OpenGL-based rendering with shader effects
  * On-screen display (OSD) support
  * Remote control via OSC, IPC, and message queues
 .
 This package includes NDI SDK libraries bundled in compliance with
 the NDI SDK license agreement. See /usr/share/doc/cuems-videocomposer/NDI-COMPLIANCE
 for details.

